@startuml
|User|
start
:Visit registration page;
:Fill in username, email, password;
:Submit form;

|Backend|
:Receive registration request;
if (Are all fields valid?) then (no)
  |User|
  :See validation error;
  :Correct input;
  :Resubmit form;
  |Backend|
  :Receive registration request;
endif

if (Does email already exist?) then (yes)
  |User|
  :See "email already in use" error;
  stop
endif

:Hash password (BCrypt);
:Save User to database;
:Return success response;

|User|
:Redirected to login page;
stop
@enduml